{
  "stem": "21310.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And also in Silesia-- that's the part where I was born-- there were many, many Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they also were for Hitler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were fights then between the Poles and the-- and the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "By the way, that's because there were so-- this part of Poland belonged to Germany before the First World War.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so my mother had a-- a German education.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- and we spoke mostly German at home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "At least, I was bilingual.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We spoke both languages.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that helped me during the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Naturally, that doesn't mean that everybody who knew German had an easier time, but in my case, it really helped quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, and just before the war broke out, there were announcements on the radios and loudspeakers that every apartment had to have one room that is airtight because, you know, gas was used in the-- during the first World War, so they expected gas to be used during this war.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So everybody had to make one room airtight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I remember my mother taping windows in one room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then she decided that the bathroom would be a better room because there were no windows.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she was taping at the doors and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were told to prepare a-- a-- a first aid kit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Everybody should have a first aid kit and that we had [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] gas masks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were buying-- people were buying gas masks, all preparing for gas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there were drills, like air raid drills so-- where we were told to go to-- but there were no shelters but like basements or sub-basements.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And when the sirens went off, everybody was practicing how to get to shelters.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
